casebody.data:
No. 09-1238. Dennis Hollingsworth, et al., Petitioners v. United States District Court for the Northern District of California, et al. 562 U.S. 801, 131 S. Ct. 372,

178 L. Ed. 2d 1,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 6478. October 4, 2010.

On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit with instructions to dismiss the case as moot. See United States v. Munsingwear, Inc., 340 U.S. 36, 71 S. Ct. 104, 95 L. Ed. 36 (1950).
